{"tid":986105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽見聲音要他攻擊？ 戰鬥民族闖紐約中餐廳鎚殺3中國人","createTime":"2019-01-18T07:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T08:12:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7699c1993aa89f55f2fcb77f810c32c25e3e5dc9","tid":986105,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QbBuH3q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQbBuH3q.png&h=558e04ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國紐約布魯克林區一名俄羅斯裔男子，15日進入一家中國人經營的自助海鮮餐廳，並用鐵鎚攻擊店內3名中國籍男子，造成1死2重傷。據了解，警方於16日下午依謀殺和企圖謀殺等多項罪名將他逮捕，並懷疑他可能患有精神疾病，將為他進行精神鑑定。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，34歲俄羅斯裔男子亞瑟（Arthur Martunovich）15日先在餐廳門口大吼大叫、打傷1名員工後，接著走到餐廳後面攻擊另1名員工，再進入廚房襲擊第3名被害者，造成來自中國福州亭江的34歲廚師逝世，以及60歲餐廳老闆和50歲經理重傷。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，餐廳內的客人見狀嚇得趕緊逃命，亞瑟後來於現場附近被捕。據了解，警方認為他的狀況十分不穩定，因為他一下子聲稱，觀看中國女性受中國男性虐待的電影後，自己要採取行動捍衛亞洲女性；但一下子又表示，聽見聲音要他襲擊陌生人，還強調這些聲音到處都是，甚至在討論外星人。目前警方仍在釐清亞瑟的作案動機，而亞瑟則被控謀殺和企圖謀殺等多項罪名，並須接受精神評估。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2675540\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2675540&d=099CS1sxW8vPw7uDUphh7cKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=a4f02f15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2675540&h=bfd1e651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2675540</a>"},{"pid":"01f1b57a7cb622a24e113aaf24fdaef25e2c9bf2","tid":986105,"uid":40470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"世上最清醒既俄佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b72257ecf76da47561ad6e0c2c916a6cb7e9b0f","tid":986105,"uid":52942,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:45:33.000Z","msg":"應該係聽到800萬港人心聲"},{"pid":"f009411cd2871da24439bc054f14862fcde8b19f","tid":986105,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:45:40.000Z","msg":"一物治一物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141803197b1400b15d6744ce987af6444f4df18f","tid":986105,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:05:37.000Z","msg":"紐約市：中立場"},{"pid":"a56b1952a6111827719dbe545a4e1e8523a8056c","tid":986105,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:07:29.000Z","msg":"三打一又點會唔夠打 中國人就係咁 唔關自己事就死都唔出手"},{"pid":"d968cc09a538967bf85b81ff09ddfe553041fea4","tid":986105,"uid":176472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"141803197b1400b15d6744ce987af6444f4df18f","tid":986105,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:05:37.000Z","msg":"紐約市：中立場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0MuJdR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0MuJdR.jpg&h=1fa99e7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ByzHiNc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FByzHiNc.jpg&h=0f3830a0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}